    "Secure Your Spot": "Choose a Plan",
    "Join the waiting list for early access to SIMY's revolutionary AI meeting assistant. Limited spots available for our beta launch.": "Create your SIMY account on the web, choose a plan, and complete subscription checkout securely with Stripe.",
    "Only 500 beta spots remaining": "Plans and billing are managed on the web",
