    "Exclusive beta features": "Use the iPhone app only when recording support is needed",
    "Start your journey with SIMY today": "Start SIMY on the web today",
    "Join thousands of forward-thinking teams already transforming their meetings with AI-powered insights.": "SIMY is a web-contracted SaaS. The app is a recording companion for teams that need it.",
    "できること": "What you can do",
    "特徴": "Features",
