    "\"Hi Tetsuo.\" — the Twin opens with a suggested question.": "\"Hola Tetsuo.\" – el Gemelo comienza con una pregunta sugerida.",
    "Scene 01. Morning check-in with the Digital Twin. It already knows what's due today.": "Escena 01. Registro matutino con el Gemelo Digital. Ya sabe lo que le toca hoy.",
