    "Common questions.": "Pertanyaan umum.",
    "Clear answers.": "Jawaban yang jelas.",
    "What kinds of work can SIMY handle?": "Jenis pekerjaan apa yang dapat ditangani SIMY?",
    "SIMY handles any knowledge work — strategy documents, research reports, data analysis, marketing copy, financial modelling, legal drafts, and more. If it can be described in a meeting or conversation, SIMY can execute it.": "SIMY menangani segala pekerjaan berbasis pengetahuan — dokumen strategi, laporan riset, analisis data, salinan pemasaran, pemodelan keuangan, draf hukum, dan lainnya. Jika bisa dijelaskan dalam rapat atau percakapan, SIMY bisa mengeksekusinya.",
    "Who is SIMY for?": "SIMY untuk siapa?",
    "SIMY is designed for everyone from listed enterprises to SMEs to individual operators. Any team or person who wants to delegate execution to AI and focus on judgment will benefit.": "SIMY dirancang untuk semua orang, mulai dari perusahaan tercatat hingga UKM dan operator individu. Setiap tim atau individu yang ingin mendelegasikan eksekusi ke AI dan fokus pada penilaian akan mendapat manfaat.",
    "Do I need to write prompts?": "Apakah saya perlu menulis prompt?",
    "No. SIMY extracts requirements, specs, and decisions directly from your meeting recordings and team conversations. You never need to write a prompt — just have your normal meetings and SIMY handles the rest.": "Tidak. SIMY mengekstrak kebutuhan, spesifikasi, dan keputusan langsung dari rekaman rapat dan percakapan tim Anda. Anda tidak perlu menulis prompt — cukup adakan rapat seperti biasa, SIMY yang mengurus sisanya.",
    "What meeting and communication tools are supported?": "Alat rapat dan komunikasi apa yang didukung?",
    "SIMY integrates with Zoom, Microsoft Teams, Slack huddles, Google Meet, and Gmail threads. Any recorded conversation or written communication can be used as input.": "SIMY terintegrasi dengan Zoom, Microsoft Teams, huddle Slack, Google Meet, dan thread Gmail. Percakapan terekam atau komunikasi tertulis apa pun dapat digunakan sebagai input.",
    "How does SIMY protect my data?": "Bagaimana SIMY melindungi data saya?",
    "Every organisation gets a dedicated, isolated database instance. On the Enterprise plan, your proprietary data is never used for training global models. SIMY uses end-to-end encryption and physical database isolation.": "Setiap organisasi mendapat instance database khusus yang terisolasi. Pada paket Enterprise, data eksklusif Anda tidak pernah digunakan untuk melatih model global. SIMY menggunakan enkripsi end-to-end dan isolasi database fisik.",
    "How does the 10,000-winner lottery work?": "How are web billing and the app separated?",
    "Create a free account — no credit card required. Every account is automatically entered into the lottery. We'll select 10,000 Founding Partners who'll get $5 in SIMY credits, 1:1 onboarding, and direct priority support. Winners are notified exclusively within the app.": "Plans, billing, and subscription management happen on the web. After checkout, create a workspace, connect integrations, and connect the iPhone recording companion only if needed.",
