    "10,000 winners get early access.": "10.000 vincitori ottengono l'accesso anticipato.",
    "Sign up for free. We'll select 10,000 Founding Partners by lottery to help us build the future of work together.": "SIMY is a web-contracted SaaS. Stripe handles subscription checkout securely, then SIMY creates your workspace.",
