    "08 / FAQ": "08 / 常见问题",
    "Common questions.": "常见问题，",
    "Clear answers.": "清晰解答。",
    "What kinds of work can SIMY handle?": "SIMY 可以处理哪些类型的工作？",
    "SIMY handles any knowledge work — strategy documents, research reports, data analysis, marketing copy, financial modelling, legal drafts, and more. If it can be described in a meeting or conversation, SIMY can execute it.": "SIMY 可处理任何知识工作——战略文档、研究报告、数据分析、营销文案、财务建模、法律草稿等等。只要能在会议或对话中描述的事情，SIMY 都能执行。",
    "Who is SIMY for?": "SIMY 适合谁使用？",
    "SIMY is designed for everyone from listed enterprises to SMEs to individual operators. Any team or person who wants to delegate execution to AI and focus on judgment will benefit.": "SIMY 面向从上市企业到中小企业再到个人经营者的所有人。任何希望将执行委托给 AI 并专注于判断的团队或个人都能从中受益。",
    "Do I need to write prompts?": "我需要写提示词吗？",
    "No. SIMY extracts requirements, specs, and decisions directly from your meeting recordings and team conversations. You never need to write a prompt — just have your normal meetings and SIMY handles the rest.": "不需要。SIMY 会直接从你的会议录音和团队对话中提取需求、规格和决策。你永远无需写提示词——只管正常开会，其余交给 SIMY。",
    "What meeting and communication tools are supported?": "支持哪些会议和沟通工具？",
    "SIMY integrates with Zoom, Microsoft Teams, Slack huddles, Google Meet, and Gmail threads. Any recorded conversation or written communication can be used as input.": "SIMY 集成 Zoom、Microsoft Teams、Slack huddles、Google Meet 和 Gmail 会话。任何录制的对话或书面沟通都可作为输入。",
    "How does SIMY protect my data?": "SIMY 如何保护我的数据？",
    "Every organisation gets a dedicated, isolated database instance. On the Enterprise plan, your proprietary data is never used for training global models. SIMY uses end-to-end encryption and physical database isolation.": "每个组织都获得一个专属的隔离数据库实例。在企业版中，你的专有数据永不用于训练全球模型。SIMY 采用端到端加密和物理数据库隔离。",
    "How does the 10,000-winner lottery work?": "How are web billing and the app separated?",
    "Create a free account — no credit card required. Every account is automatically entered into the lottery. We'll select 10,000 Founding Partners who'll get $5 in SIMY credits, 1:1 onboarding, and direct priority support. Winners are notified exclusively within the app.": "Plans, billing, and subscription management happen on the web. After checkout, create a workspace, connect integrations, and connect the iPhone recording companion only if needed.",
    "Now Accepting Applications": "正在接受申请",
    "AI execution starts": "AI 执行",
    "the moment you join.": "在你加入的那一刻开始。",
    "Talk to Sales": "联系销售",
    "Enterprise plans available · No credit card required": "Enterprise plans available · Billing is managed on the web",
