    "Persona 04 / role-based": "女神异闻录 04 / 基于角色",
    "Taken verbatim from the SIMY Home page — persona 04 of 9. The Product Manager at a 150-person tech company. No name, just the role and the story.": "逐字摘自 SIMY 主页 — 角色 04（共 9 个）。一家拥有 150 名员工的科技公司的产品经理。没有名字，只有角色和故事。",
    "Planning ends. Real work begins.": "计划结束。真正的工作开始了。",
    "After every planning session, someone spends hours turning discussion into a structured roadmap. Decisions get lost. Owners get fuzzy. The doc lands in Notion by Thursday.": "每次计划会议结束后，都会有人花几个小时将讨论变成结构化的路线图。决策会迷失。业主变得模糊。该文档将于周四抵达 Notion。",
    "Meeting ends. Roadmap ships.": "会议结束。路线图船舶。",
    "SIMY generates a structured roadmap, assigns owners, and sends summaries automatically. Every decision is captured the moment it's made — no cleanup required.": "SIMY 生成结构化路线图、分配所有者并自动发送摘要。每个决定在做出时都会被捕获 - 无需清理。",
