    "before the next standup.": "在下一次站立之前。",
    "Her squads show up to standup with a shared, written plan — not a half-remembered meeting. Mondays are now about questions, not note-taking.": "她的团队会拿出一份共同的书面计划，而不是一次记不清的会议。周一现在是提问，而不是做笔记。",
