    "See SIMY in action through the eyes of the Product Manager from our Home page. Meeting → actions → dashboard → digital twin, played back like Screen Studio.": "从我们的主页上通过产品经理的视角查看 SIMY 的实际应用。会议 → 操作 → 仪表板 → 数字孪生，像 Screen Studio 一样回放。",
    "SIMY Demo — The Product Manager's story": "SIMY 演示 — 产品经理的故事",
