    "Move work before it piles up": "加载前移动",
    "People are short. Work keeps growing. SIMY moves.": "人不够啊Work will increase.西米动了。",
    "People are short.": "人不够啊",
    "Work keeps growing.": "工作量将会增加。",
    "SIMY moves.": "SIMY moves.",
    "Attrition, transfers, hiring freezes, and double-duty roles keep adding management work to the same capable people. SIMY moves meeting operations, progress checks, urgent responses, monthly reports, OJT, and procedure drafts before they pile up, then returns the final judgment to humans.": "退休、调动、冻结招聘、兼任。 Even though the number of people will not increase, the burden of meeting management, progress confirmation, emergency response, monthly reporting, OJT, and procedure manual creation will be placed on specific people. Twin在将管理工作交给人类之前处理好，并且只将最终的决定返回给人类。",
    "People are short. Work keeps growing.": "人不够啊工作量将会增加。",
    "SIMY moves": "To those who can",
    "the management work": "日积月累的管理工作，",
    "before it piles up.": "SIMY 首先行动。",
    "When teams cover departures, transfers, double-duty roles, and hiring freezes, meetings, management, training, reporting, and urgent responses collect around a few people. SIMY moves that work forward so the department does not stall.": "会议、管理、培训、报告和应急响应将通过填补退休人员和调动人员的空缺、保留额外职位以及冻结招聘等方式集中于特定人员。 Twin 继续推进行政工作以维持部门的运转，并将其从那些有能力的人手中夺走。",
    "Show 3 more": "查看更多 3 件商品",
    "Meeting operations and progress checks": "会议管理/进度确认",
    "Weekly meetings, department coordination, team progress, and teammate instructions keep moving.": "永远不要停止召开每周会议、组织部门、检查团队进度以及向下属/同事发出指示。",
    "Planning, priorities, and resource alignment": "规划、优先事项和资源协调",
    "Budgets, long-term plans, priority calls, and no-new-headcount tradeoffs become decision-ready.": "我们将使用预算管理、长期规划、优先顺序和调整，前提是它们不会被用作帮助您做出决策的材料。",
    "Customer and urgent response": "客户/紧急响应",
    "Email complaints, urgent issues, and direct customer requests advance all the way to a reply draft.": "我们将通过电子邮件回复客户的投诉、紧急事项和直接沟通，并进行回复建议。",
    "Training and knowledge sharing": "教育/知识共享",
    "New-hire explanations, OJT, Q&A, internal sharing, and recovery support stop depending on one person.": "我们不对新员工进行解释、OJT、回答问题、团队内分享、后续跟进等未能做到个性化的情况。",
    "Procedures, handoffs, and FAQs": "程序/转移/常见问题解答",
    "Screenshot procedures, manuals, FAQs, and handoff material stop waiting for someone to write them.": "截图的流程手册、业务手册、常见问题解答、交接材料不会停止等待创建。",
    "Reporting, meetings, and task assignment": "报告/会议/任务分配",
    "Weekly CEO reports, monthly CFO updates, cross-team meetings, and task assignments get drafted.": "起草首席执行官的周报告、首席财务官的月报告、跨职能会议和任务分配。",
    "The 10/90 rule": "彻底执行10/90规则",
    "Focus on the top 10%": "产生 90% 的结果，",
    "that creates 90% of the result.": "重点关注前 10%。",
    "SIMY identifies the work outside the highest-leverage 10%, prepares owners, deadlines, monthly report inputs, customer follow-up email drafts, procedures, and documents, and leaves humans free to focus on the non-linear decisions AI cannot replace.": "Twin利用人工智能来识别产生90%结果的“前10%重要事项”以外的事项，并提前准备好会议确定的职责和期限、月报材料、客户跟进电子邮件文本以及流程手册和材料的草稿。我们人类只能关注AI无法取代的10%的“不连续增长”。",
