    "Common questions.": "常見問題，",
    "Clear answers.": "清晰解答。",
    "What kinds of work can SIMY handle?": "SIMY 可以處理哪些類型的工作？",
    "SIMY handles any knowledge work — strategy documents, research reports, data analysis, marketing copy, financial modelling, legal drafts, and more. If it can be described in a meeting or conversation, SIMY can execute it.": "SIMY 可處理任何知識工作——策略文件、研究報告、資料分析、行銷文案、財務建模、法律草稿等等。只要能在會議或對話中描述的事情，SIMY 都能執行。",
    "Who is SIMY for?": "SIMY 適合誰使用？",
    "SIMY is designed for everyone from listed enterprises to SMEs to individual operators. Any team or person who wants to delegate execution to AI and focus on judgment will benefit.": "SIMY 面向從上市企業到中小企業再到個人經營者的所有人。任何希望將執行委任給 AI 並專注於判斷的團隊或個人都能從中受益。",
    "Do I need to write prompts?": "我需要寫提示詞嗎？",
    "No. SIMY extracts requirements, specs, and decisions directly from your meeting recordings and team conversations. You never need to write a prompt — just have your normal meetings and SIMY handles the rest.": "不需要。SIMY 會直接從你的會議錄音和團隊對話中萃取需求、規格和決策。你永遠無需寫提示詞——只管正常開會，其餘交給 SIMY。",
    "What meeting and communication tools are supported?": "支援哪些會議和溝通工具？",
    "SIMY integrates with Zoom, Microsoft Teams, Slack huddles, Google Meet, and Gmail threads. Any recorded conversation or written communication can be used as input.": "SIMY 整合 Zoom、Microsoft Teams、Slack huddles、Google Meet 和 Gmail 討論串。任何錄製的對話或書面溝通都可作為輸入。",
    "How does SIMY protect my data?": "SIMY 如何保護我的資料？",
    "Every organisation gets a dedicated, isolated database instance. On the Enterprise plan, your proprietary data is never used for training global models. SIMY uses end-to-end encryption and physical database isolation.": "每個組織都獲得一個專屬的隔離資料庫實例。在企業版中，您的專有資料永不用於訓練全球模型。SIMY 採用端到端加密和實體資料庫隔離。",
    "How does the 10,000-winner lottery work?": "Web 帳單和 App 如何分開？",
    "Create a free account — no credit card required. Every account is automatically entered into the lottery. We'll select 10,000 Founding Partners who'll get $5 in SIMY credits, 1:1 onboarding, and direct priority support. Winners are notified exclusively within the app.": "方案、帳單與訂閱管理都在 Web 上完成。結帳後建立工作區、連接整合；只有需要時再連接 iPhone 錄音輔助 App。",
