    "Structured roadmap, owners, estimates — auto": "結構化路線圖、所有者、估算 — 汽車",
    "Before standup": "站立前",
    "Roadmap is already shared": "路線圖已分享",
    "Home page": "首頁",
    "Persona 04 / role-based": "女神異聞錄 04 / 基於角色",
    "Taken verbatim from the SIMY Home page — persona 04 of 9. The Product Manager at a 150-person tech company. No name, just the role and the story.": "逐字摘自 SIMY 首頁 — 角色 04（共 9 個）。一家擁有 150 名員工的科技公司的產品經理。沒有名字，只有角色和故事。",
    "Planning ends. Real work begins.": "計劃結束。真正的工作開始了。",
    "After every planning session, someone spends hours turning discussion into a structured roadmap. Decisions get lost. Owners get fuzzy. The doc lands in Notion by Thursday.": "每次規劃會議結束後，都會有人花幾個小時將討論變成結構化的路線圖。決策會迷失。業主變得模糊。該文檔將於週四抵達 Notion。",
    "Meeting ends. Roadmap ships.": "會議結束。路線圖船舶。",
    "SIMY generates a structured roadmap, assigns owners, and sends summaries automatically. Every decision is captured the moment it's made — no cleanup required.": "SIMY 產生結構化路線圖、分配所有者並自動發送摘要。每個決定在做出時都會被捕獲 - 無需清理。",
    "The outcome": "結果",
    "Roadmap ready": "路線圖已準備好",
    "before the next standup.": "在下一次站立之前。",
    "Her squads show up to standup with a shared, written plan — not a half-remembered meeting. Mondays are now about questions, not note-taking.": "她的團隊會拿出一份共同的書面計劃，而不是一次記不清的會議。週一現在是提問，而不是做筆記。",
    "02 / Demo": "02 / 演示",
    "Her Tuesday afternoon,": "她週二下午，",
    "played back in 12 seconds.": "12秒後播放。",
    "A single unbroken take through the real SIMY desktop app. Four scenes — Meeting, Actions, Dashboard, Twin — with the cursor moving the way she moves it. No edits, no fake UI.": "一次不間斷地瀏覽真正的 SIMY 桌面應用程式。四個場景——會議、動作、儀表板、雙胞胎——遊標隨著她移動的方式移動。沒有編輯，沒有假UI。",
