    "Attrition, transfers, hiring freezes, and double-duty roles keep adding management work to the same capable people. SIMY moves meeting operations, progress checks, urgent responses, monthly reports, OJT, and procedure drafts before they pile up, then returns the final judgment to humans.": "退休、調動、凍結招募、兼任。即使人數不會增加，但會議管理、進度確認、緊急應變、每月報告、在職培訓、流程手冊製作等負擔將由特定人員承擔。 Twin在將管理工作交給人類之前處理好，並且只將最終的決定回饋給人類。",
    "People are short. Work keeps growing.": "人不夠啊工作量將會增加。",
