    "before it piles up.": "SIMY 首先行動。",
    "When teams cover departures, transfers, double-duty roles, and hiring freezes, meetings, management, training, reporting, and urgent responses collect around a few people. SIMY moves that work forward so the department does not stall.": "會議、管理、培訓、報告和緊急應變將透過填補退休人員和調動人員的空缺、保留額外職位以及凍結招聘等方式集中於特定人員。 Twin 繼續推動行政工作以維持部門的運轉，並將其從那些有能力的人手中奪走。",
    "Show 3 more": "查看更多 3 件商品",
