    "Weekly meetings, department coordination, team progress, and teammate instructions keep moving.": "永遠不要停止召開每週會議、組織部門、檢查團隊進度以及向下屬/同事發出指示。",
    "Planning, priorities, and resource alignment": "規劃、優先事項和資源協調",
    "Budgets, long-term plans, priority calls, and no-new-headcount tradeoffs become decision-ready.": "我們將使用預算管理、長期規劃、優先順序和調整，前提是它們不會被用作幫助您做出決策的材料。",
